structure.unit: TRAFFIC REGULATIONS -- VEHICLE EQUIPMENT AND STORAGE

law.history: Repealed 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 93, sec. 12. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2739g-38, 2896a-15.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Ambulances, patrols, and fire apparatus to have right of way.
